    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a documented VANOS overhaul. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, paired with a refreshed subframe\u2014reinforced to exceed factory specifications. Every bushing has been replaced with OEM+ components for razor-sharp turn-in, while the factory limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent throughout, showing zero evidence of track use or thermal stress. This is a mechanically synchronized masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
