      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin feels and smells like new; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since the first mile. Every electronic component functions flawlessly, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented at certified dealerships. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or oxidation. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning collector who demands perfection. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
